    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the applicability of the MPLS Transport Profile (MPLS-TP) with use case studies and network design considerations.  The use cases include Metro Ethernet access and aggregation transport, mobile backhaul, and packet optical transport.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
